  m_EditorHideFlags: 0
  m_Script: {fileID: 11500000, guid: 0f832b14936fc2048824d9308b14ded6, type: 3}
  m_Name: AfterPixel
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  allLines:
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "So, Elroi... I wanted to ask you about your past relationships. I
      know it\u2019s kind of a shitty topic but it is something I value knowing as
      a Venusian and as a person as well.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Ask away babe, I am an honest man. But you might not like what you
      hear.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "See, you probably won\u2019t either. I recently went through a breakup.
      It wasn\u2019t a bad one, we agreed to keep things friendly but the problem
      was that... it just didn\u2019t last for a long time.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "I don\u2019t see a problem with that.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "And I don\u2019t mean to scare you because I do wanna see where..
      this might lead but the thing is I never manage to make things last- wait.
      What do you mean?\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Well, I know we are doing this program bullshit, whatever, Chaperon
      cover your ears.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 3
    characterName: Chaperon
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "I am sorry, I can\u2019t do that.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Okay, fuck you then. Anyways, I know we are here to \u201Cfind love\u201D
      and shit but I\u2019ve never really been too good at that whole biz.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Well, me neither.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "You know you are way more chill and a lot funnier than most women
      I\u2019ve been with.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: '..Oh..kay?

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'And I do enjoy talking to you.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Uh-huh.



'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "But I\u2019m not gonna marry you.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'OH GOD NO! HAHA! Well, I mean, marriage was never my intention going
      into this anyway. But I guess I was hoping that this would somehow... fix me,
      or something.

'
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Yeah it\u2019s not like the government has ever let you down before.\r\n\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "That might be the smartest thing you\u2019ve said so far. "
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 'Thank you. '
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Hmm.. Ah, whatever. I really don\u2019t know what I was expecting.
      You want more drinks? "
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "\u2018Course I do. "
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 0
    characterName: Io
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "Ah, I wish I had siblings. I\u2019ve kind of had a lonely childhood. "
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: "You know, Yova might be the only person I can talk to for hours and
      hours without getting bored. She\u2019s truly amazing.\r\n"
    eventTrigger: 
    choices: []
  - side: 1
    characterName: Elroi
    characterSprite: {fileID: 0}
    sentence: 
    eventTrigger: 
    choices:
    - choices: What does she do for a living?
      nextScenario: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 7d42679ed2723af4aa76acc1be2ad1b0, type: 2}
      target: 0
      starReward: 0
      heartReward: 0
    - choices: "I\u2019m guessing your sister never taught you how to talk to girls?"
      nextScenario: {fileID: 11400000, guid: bc9acd0af81f7e64786e952fc8708ebe, type: 2}
      target: 0
      starReward: 0
      heartReward: 0
    - choices: Has she ever bullied the shit out of you?
      nextScenario: {fileID: 11400000, guid: 08bf9546d247e464a9e1120562767a59, type: 2}
      target: 0
      starReward: 0
